                        <origin>Habisfern</origin>
                        <genre>Fantasy</genre>
                    </information>

                    <description>
                        <short>
                            Earth elementals are creatures of earth and
                            rock.
                        </short>

                        <physical>
                            <para>
                                Looking like a large human with stony skin,
                                this type of elemental is strong and tough.
                                It's arms end in three fingered hands which
                                are little use for anything other than basic
                                grasping or smashing.
                            </para>
                        </physical>
                    </description>

                    <statistics xmlns="http://yagsbook.sourceforge.net/xml/yags">
